title: Printer's Sample Book (USA), 1883–84
creditline: Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts
description: Small leather notebook with handwritten formulas for dyestuffs for printed textiles. Contains 160 samples of printed fabric.

tombstone.epitaph: Printer's Sample Book (USA), 1883–84; Manufactured by Old Pacific Print Works ; leather, cardboard, cotton; Gift of Frederick J. Whitehead from the collection compiled by his father Cornelius Whitehead at the Pacific Print Works of Lawrence, Massachusetts; 1945-55-22
